Corrosion resistant mirror-like finish reduces exhaust gas pressure and enhances the performance of the exhaust system, making your vehicle more efficient.
Easy to install with professional-grade clamps or banding. No welding required.
Magnaflow stainless steel exhaust pipe is 100% stainless steel throughout, not just the liner like many of the competition. 
Warranty:
Magnaflow Stainless Steel Exhaust Tips are backed by a lifetime warranty.
